java.lang.IllegalArgumentException: Duplicate enchantment id! class rafradek.blocklauncher.EnchantmentShrinkBL and class zotmc.tomahawk.ench.EnchReplica Enchantment ID:143

不过考虑到reika的mod引入那么多id，还不知道会出什么幺蛾子呢。
